#########################
# pablocb2303@gmail.com #
#########################

IMAPAccount pablocb2303@gmail.com
Host imap.gmail.com
User pablocb2303@gmail.com
AuthMechs XOAUTH2
PassCmd "$XDG_CONFIG_HOME/mutt/mutt_oauth2.py $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/mutt/tokens/pablocb2303@gmail.com.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore pablocb2303@gmail.com-remote
Account pablocb2303@gmail.com

MaildirStore pablocb2303@gmail.com-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/pablocb2303@gmail.com/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/pablocb2303@gmail.com/Inbox

Channel pablocb2303@gmail.com
Far :pablocb2303@gmail.com-remote:
Near :pablocb2303@gmail.com-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *


